{"tid":1980044,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"文宣/連儂/想幫手但唔敢做嘅寶寶入一入嚟","createTime":"2020-04-20T00:04:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T04:03:19.000Z","uid":281352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"394ebb1d53cb5892deb5f57cafc0283bdeedc106","tid":1980044,"uid":281352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T00:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鑑於而家整<span style=\"color: purple;\">連儂牆</span>愈來愈<span style=\"color: purple;\">風險高回報低</span><br />\n1.彩印成本高<br />\n2.手足要承擔被捕的風險<br />\n3.轉頭就被藍絲撕走<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小弟有以下嘅建議：<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">1.印文宣幫有地舖嘅黃店裝修</span><br />\n我哋用懲罰cover返黃店被狗搞嘅風險或損失。大家當租地方賣廣告，見有文宣就幫襯，唔好鬥黃/批鬥人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">2.靠學生哥手足多share新聞感染身邊人</span><br />\n始終學生思想未咁僵化，又比較容易接納新事物，算係<span style=\"color: purple;\">較高回報</span>嘅宣傳受眾。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文宣方向：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">1.政府腐敗</span><br />\n例如：大白象工程、政府官員貪污或隱瞞利益<br />\n（好多人中老年人無睇新聞，唔知道）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">2.中國政府泯滅人性嘅罪行</span><br />\n例如：8964、一孩政策殺嬰罪行、毒奶粉官商勾結荼毒中國無數嬰兒、新疆集中營<br />\n（年輕一代好多都未睇過呢啲新聞）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">3.歷史、價值觀及邏輯思考教育</span><br />\n例如：黨不等於國家，愛國係要愛人民，而唔係愛壓迫人民嘅政府 / 中國無法治無財產權，國家隨時可以充公你嘅財產，有錢都無用<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">4.警暴</span><br />\n例如：721、逼人道歉、除女仔裙錄影<br />\n（For黃絲，「不想回憶，未敢忘記」，保持運動熱度）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n注意事項：<br />\n1.圖文並茂<br />\n2.引用數字<br />\n3.引用新聞<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">4.設計文宣時要由普通人角度思考，等大家易入口</span><br />\n即係諗下點令人容易啲轉黃。好似傳教咁，唔好一開始就叫人悔改/講耶穌愛你。三唔識七，無人會care耶穌。我哋應該要俾一個理由（多啲資訊）人哋去改變下自己嘅思想/立場，例如係令佢哋知道中國政府無人性，成日殘害百姓，總有一天輪到我哋俾中國搞，所以我哋而家就要反抗定先。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dfa2680451e514e9146bfdca1e3647712e9bed4","tid":1980044,"uid":281352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T04:02:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b3901771154fc258c8a5dc153af0da048c7d649","tid":1980044,"uid":281352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T04:03:19.000Z","msg":"想推推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}